  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Introduction:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to \"<strong>Immortal Farmer: System’s Mandate</strong>\", a paradise blending adventure, cultivation, and rural life. In this apocalyptic world overrun by demons, you are transmigrated into a refugee and stumble upon a mysterious village—Taoyuan Village, protected by cultivators.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Official Bilibili Space: 1113796124</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can enter this number after your Bilibili personal space URL,or copy the BV number: BV1NZghz3EPK and paste it directly after the main bilibili URL to jump to it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Gameplay:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>System & Cultivation:</strong> Rule your fate with the System. Awaken talents to shatter traditional limits. Master powerful skills and forge an invincible legend on the ever-changing battlefield.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb10bc0cf93941d8f68c534b60399e6f.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb10bc0cf93941d8f68c534b60399e6f.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb10bc0cf93941d8f68c534b60399e6f.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farming and Planting:</strong> Escape the chaos and find peace in the soil. Tend to your crops daily and watch them flourish. Let the rhythm of nature heal your soul and make you forget the world’s troubles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/763c2441d7808bd3f564269b416d0585.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/763c2441d7808bd3f564269b416d0585.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/763c2441d7808bd3f564269b416d0585.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration & Combat:</strong> A \"weak\" farmer? Not with the System. Slay gods and demons in bizarre forbidden realms. With randomized talents and divine skills, unleash total domination upon your foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/7682dfaf40a04ee193078a167d7155bc.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/7682dfaf40a04ee193078a167d7155bc.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/7682dfaf40a04ee193078a167d7155bc.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cultivation & Breakthrough</strong>：Immortality is a gamble with death. When Qi peaks and explodes, a mortal transcends. The System guides your energy, but your heart must face the inner demons. Stay focused to unlock supreme power；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/b17c21da7fc380cfac175f77443aaf77.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/b17c21da7fc380cfac175f77443aaf77.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/b17c21da7fc380cfac175f77443aaf77.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fail, and your soul shatters. Total ruin in a single breath.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/871dd57b239064b65f4162035638048b.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/871dd57b239064b65f4162035638048b.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/871dd57b239064b65f4162035638048b.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bonds & Trials：</strong>Every task weaves your fate in this land. While fighting for survival, your choices will sway the hearts of the maidens around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb6cea517658e881a45d791d97bf87a6.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb6cea517658e881a45d791d97bf87a6.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb6cea517658e881a45d791d97bf87a6.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Max out affection for rare treasures and moonlit secrets. Unlock heart-racing bonds and intimate moments hidden in the dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0a27fe030c48b4ab1def6bdd2bb3bb9e.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0a27fe030c48b4ab1def6bdd2bb3bb9e.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0a27fe030c48b4ab1def6bdd2bb3bb9e.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fishing & Discovery：</strong>Find peace in every ripple. From exotic fish to hidden loot, every cast is a new adventure. Explore the waters and reel in the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/1be1e19464f1cae307d762f7ca219d1c.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/1be1e19464f1cae307d762f7ca219d1c.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/1be1e19464f1cae307d762f7ca219d1c.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings:</strong>Your choices shape the story. Every decision creates a new path, leading to a destiny only you can determine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/c5107c339ad69df8d1b9a7190171f19e.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/c5107c339ad69df8d1b9a7190171f19e.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/c5107c339ad69df8d1b9a7190171f19e.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices shape your fate and the village's future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/5237f779755e57decb54bdb52ad1a4c9.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/5237f779755e57decb54bdb52ad1a4c9.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/5237f779755e57decb54bdb52ad1a4c9.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Heartbeats & Secrets：</strong>A risky game of love and lies. Balance multiple bonds while walking on thin ice. Beware—the possessive heroine has already seen through your every disguise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/664660354b407df19bed0923ea7ab611.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/664660354b407df19bed0923ea7ab611.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/664660354b407df19bed0923ea7ab611.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gear & Arsenal：</strong>Wield divine weapons and don legendary armor to survive with honor. Explore forbidden zones not just to survive, but to scavenge powerful ancient sets lost in a shattered world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0658745ae9b2905adfeff2e8aa69f6fb.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0658745ae9b2905adfeff2e8aa69f6fb.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0658745ae9b2905adfeff2e8aa69f6fb.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cultivator Protection:</strong> Taoyuan Village is protected by cultivators, filled with mystery and ancient traditions. Here, you will learn various cultivation knowledge and enhance your abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Female Character Interaction:</strong> Each female character has a unique personality and background story. Interacting with them will bring you rich emotional experiences. Increasing favorability not only grants rewards but also unlocks more storylines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Authentic Farming Experience:</strong> The farming system in the game realistically simulates the processes of planting, watering, and harvesting, allowing you to truly feel the joy and sense of achievement of farming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pleasure of Water Area Exploration:</strong> The vast and mysterious water areas on the map hide new fish and treasures with every exploration. Fishing is not only a leisurely activity but also a challenge and adventure.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Introduction:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to \"<strong>Immortal Farmer: System’s Mandate</strong>\", a paradise blending adventure, cultivation, and rural life. In this apocalyptic world overrun by demons, you are transmigrated into a refugee and stumble upon a mysterious village—Taoyuan Village, protected by cultivators.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Official Bilibili Space: 1113796124</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can enter this number after your Bilibili personal space URL,or copy the BV number: BV1NZghz3EPK and paste it directly after the main bilibili URL to jump to it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Gameplay:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>System & Cultivation:</strong> Rule your fate with the System. Awaken talents to shatter traditional limits. Master powerful skills and forge an invincible legend on the ever-changing battlefield.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb10bc0cf93941d8f68c534b60399e6f.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb10bc0cf93941d8f68c534b60399e6f.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb10bc0cf93941d8f68c534b60399e6f.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farming and Planting:</strong> Escape the chaos and find peace in the soil. Tend to your crops daily and watch them flourish. Let the rhythm of nature heal your soul and make you forget the world’s troubles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/763c2441d7808bd3f564269b416d0585.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/763c2441d7808bd3f564269b416d0585.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/763c2441d7808bd3f564269b416d0585.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration & Combat:</strong> A \"weak\" farmer? Not with the System. Slay gods and demons in bizarre forbidden realms. With randomized talents and divine skills, unleash total domination upon your foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/7682dfaf40a04ee193078a167d7155bc.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/7682dfaf40a04ee193078a167d7155bc.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/7682dfaf40a04ee193078a167d7155bc.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cultivation & Breakthrough</strong>：Immortality is a gamble with death. When Qi peaks and explodes, a mortal transcends. The System guides your energy, but your heart must face the inner demons. Stay focused to unlock supreme power；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/b17c21da7fc380cfac175f77443aaf77.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/b17c21da7fc380cfac175f77443aaf77.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/b17c21da7fc380cfac175f77443aaf77.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fail, and your soul shatters. Total ruin in a single breath.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/871dd57b239064b65f4162035638048b.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/871dd57b239064b65f4162035638048b.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/871dd57b239064b65f4162035638048b.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bonds & Trials：</strong>Every task weaves your fate in this land. While fighting for survival, your choices will sway the hearts of the maidens around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb6cea517658e881a45d791d97bf87a6.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb6cea517658e881a45d791d97bf87a6.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb6cea517658e881a45d791d97bf87a6.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Max out affection for rare treasures and moonlit secrets. Unlock heart-racing bonds and intimate moments hidden in the dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0a27fe030c48b4ab1def6bdd2bb3bb9e.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0a27fe030c48b4ab1def6bdd2bb3bb9e.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0a27fe030c48b4ab1def6bdd2bb3bb9e.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fishing & Discovery：</strong>Find peace in every ripple. From exotic fish to hidden loot, every cast is a new adventure. Explore the waters and reel in the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/1be1e19464f1cae307d762f7ca219d1c.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/1be1e19464f1cae307d762f7ca219d1c.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/1be1e19464f1cae307d762f7ca219d1c.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings:</strong>Your choices shape the story. Every decision creates a new path, leading to a destiny only you can determine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/c5107c339ad69df8d1b9a7190171f19e.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/c5107c339ad69df8d1b9a7190171f19e.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/c5107c339ad69df8d1b9a7190171f19e.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices shape your fate and the village's future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/5237f779755e57decb54bdb52ad1a4c9.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/5237f779755e57decb54bdb52ad1a4c9.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/5237f779755e57decb54bdb52ad1a4c9.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Heartbeats & Secrets：</strong>A risky game of love and lies. Balance multiple bonds while walking on thin ice. Beware—the possessive heroine has already seen through your every disguise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/664660354b407df19bed0923ea7ab611.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/664660354b407df19bed0923ea7ab611.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/664660354b407df19bed0923ea7ab611.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gear & Arsenal：</strong>Wield divine weapons and don legendary armor to survive with honor. Explore forbidden zones not just to survive, but to scavenge powerful ancient sets lost in a shattered world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0658745ae9b2905adfeff2e8aa69f6fb.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0658745ae9b2905adfeff2e8aa69f6fb.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0658745ae9b2905adfeff2e8aa69f6fb.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cultivator Protection:</strong> Taoyuan Village is protected by cultivators, filled with mystery and ancient traditions. Here, you will learn various cultivation knowledge and enhance your abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Female Character Interaction:</strong> Each female character has a unique personality and background story. Interacting with them will bring you rich emotional experiences. Increasing favorability not only grants rewards but also unlocks more storylines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Authentic Farming Experience:</strong> The farming system in the game realistically simulates the processes of planting, watering, and harvesting, allowing you to truly feel the joy and sense of achievement of farming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pleasure of Water Area Exploration:</strong> The vast and mysterious water areas on the map hide new fish and treasures with every exploration. Fishing is not only a leisurely activity but also a challenge and adventure.</p></li></ul>",
